column5: Will be going up to Savant Lake area and was wondering if there has been enough rain to bring the water levels up. Last year was the worst I have seen in the 25 years our group has been going up. Slugger
LOTS......... 7 inches last week. I think 20 inches in the last month or so.
SLUGGER Just got back from Savant Lake,the rain has been almost non-stop since early june and the water level is higher than they have seen in the past 28 years.
